      <div class="meta">By <strong>Robert Arthur</strong> — formatted for Class 10 CBSE NCERT. Sections are collapsible/expandable.</div>
    </header>

    <div class="controls" role="toolbar" aria-label="Expand or collapse all sections">
      <button id="expandAll" type="button" title="Open all sections">Expand All</button>
      <button id="collapseAll" type="button" title="Close all sections">Collapse All</button>
